  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 2nd level, a brawler becomes skilled at forcefully moving his opponent\
    \ around the battlefield. The brawler gains a +1 bonus on bull rush, drag, and\
    \ reposition combat maneuver checks. The brawler also gains a +1 bonus to CMD\
    \ when attacked with the bull rush, drag, and reposition maneuvers. These bonuses\
    \ increase by +1 for every four levels after 2nd (to a maximum of +5 at 18th level)."
  effects: null
